title: 2016–17 Regional One Day Cup
text:
The 2016–17 Regional One Day Cup was a <a href="List%20A%20cricket">List A</a> cricket tournament in <a href="Pakistan">Pakistan</a>. The competition ran from 8 to 27 January 2017. The final was played between <a href="Karachi%20Whites">Karachi Whites</a> and <a href="Peshawar%20cricket%20team">Peshawar</a>, with Peshawar winning by 124 runs.
